# ============================================
# INSTAGRAM API (Para mostrar feed en home)
# ============================================
# Instagram Basic Display API
# Setup: https://developers.facebook.com/docs/instagram-basic-display-api
# 
# Pasos:
#   1. Crear app en https://developers.facebook.com
#   2. Agregar producto "Instagram Basic Display"
#   3. Configurar OAuth Redirect URI: http://localhost:3000/api/instagram/callback
#   4. Obtener App ID y App Secret
#   5. Autorizar app y obtener access token
#   6. Intercambiar por long-lived token (60 d√≠as)
#
# Ver gu√≠a completa: docs/INSTAGRAM_INTEGRATION.md
INSTAGRAM_APP_ID=tu_app_id
INSTAGRAM_APP_SECRET=tu_app_secret
INSTAGRAM_ACCESS_TOKEN=tu_long_lived_token
# Nota: INSTAGRAM_REDIRECT_URI se construye autom√°ticamente usando NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL + '/api/instagram/callback'

# ============================================
# VERCEL API (Para actualizaci√≥n autom√°tica de token)
# ============================================
# Configuraci√≥n para que el cron job actualice autom√°ticamente
# el token de Instagram en Vercel cada 50 d√≠as
#
# Pasos:
#   1. Crear token en: https://vercel.com/account/tokens
#   2. Obtener Project ID: Settings ‚Üí General ‚Üí Project ID
#   3. Team ID (opcional): Solo si es proyecto de team
#   4. Generar CRON_SECRET: openssl rand -base64 32
#
# Ver gu√≠a completa: docs/INSTAGRAM_AUTO_REFRESH.md
VERCEL_TOKEN=tu_vercel_api_token
VERCEL_PROJECT_ID=tu_project_id
